Name: Seiko Men's Presage Classic Automatic SPB463J Watch
Description: The Seiko Presage Classic Automatic Watch is a showcase of Japanese artistry and precision, influenced by the past. With a stainless steel case and bracelet, the softly textured dial is inspired by Japanese silk fabric, and reflects ambient light. Powered by the movement of the wearer, it's water resistant to 100 meters.

Name: Seiko Men's Prospex Sea Automatic Divers SPB453J Watch
Description: Inspired by the legendary and original 1965 Divers Watch, the Seiko Men's Prospex Sea Divers Watch is a functional and reliable timepiece. A stainless steel case and bracelet is finished with a black dial and date display. With a water resistance to 300 meters, it features LumiBrite hands and markers to ensure high legibility even in dark conditions.

Name: Two-Tone Men's Chronograph Watch in Blue Tone Stainless Steel
Description: Discover sophistication in our stainless steel and blue tone 44mm chronograph quartz watch. Water-resistant up to 100m, it's a timeless statement of style.

Name: Men's 0.60 Carat TW Diamond Quartz Yellow Gold Tone Stainless Steel Watch with Black Dial
Description: Experience timeless elegance with our yellow gold-tone stainless steel watch, featuring 0.60 total carat weight diamonds encircling the black dial. With a quartz battery, 50m water resistance, and sapphire crystal, it's a symbol of luxury.

Name: Men's 0.60 Carat TW Diamond Quartz Stainless Steel Watch with Blue Dial
Description: Elevate your style with our stainless steel watch, with 0.60 total carat weight diamonds around the blue dial. With a 43mm design, folding clasp, 50m water resistance, and sapphire crystal, it's a symbol of modern luxury.

Name: Men's Chronograph Stainless Steel Watch with Black Dial
Description: Elevate your style with our stainless steel 44mm chronograph quartz watch with a black dial. Water-resistant up to 100m, it's a statement of modern sophistication.

Name: Two-Tone Men's Chronograph Watch in Gold Tone Stainless Steel
Description: Embrace modern luxury with our 44mm two-tone chronograph quartz watch in yellow gold-tone stainless steel with a black dial. With 100m water resistance and a domed crystal face, it's a timeless essential.

Name: Men's Automatic Two-Tone Watch in Blue Tone Stainless Steel
Description: Embrace sophistication with our blue-tone stainless steel 44mm automatic watch. Water-resistant up to 200m, it's a symbol of timeless elegance.

Name: Two-Tone Men's 0.60 Carat TW Diamond Quartz Watch in Yellow Gold Tone Stainless Steel
Description: Elevate your everyday style with our stainless steel and diamond watch, with 0.60 total carat weight diamonds around the watch face. Featuring a 43mm design, folding clasp, and 50m water resistance.

Name: Seiko Men's Presage Cocktail Time Automatic SRPE19J Watch
Description: Both functional and modern, the Seiko Presage Cocktail Time Skydiving Watch offers Japanese beauty and quality. With a stainless steel case and bracelet, the watch features a blue textured sunburst dial that reflects the light. Powered by the movement of the wearer, it's the perfect addition to any collection.

Name: Seiko Men's Prospex Sea Automatic Divers SPB451 Watch
Description: In the decades since it introduced Japan’s first divers watch, Seiko has won the favour of professionals and enthusiasts worldwide for their safety, reliability, and ease of use. The Seiko Men's Prospex Sea Automatic Divers Watch features a stainless steel case and bracelet, a blue dial with a date display, and a tachymeter. Water resistant to 300 meters, it's finished with LumiBright hands and markers to ensure high legibility in dark conditions.

Name: Seiko Men's Presage Classic Automatic SPB471J Watch
Description: Melding Japanese artistry with longstanding mastery of mechanical watchmaking, the Seiko Presage Classic Automatic Watch showcases elegance and tradition. With a stainless steel case and bracelet, the black dial is inspired by Japanese silk fabric, reflecting ambient light. Water resistant to 100 meters, it features automatic movement powered by the wearer, and an open-heart sub-dial that showcases the intricacy of the movement.

Name: Seiko Presage Men's Automatic SPB469J
Description: Melding Japanese artistry with Seiko's longstanding mastery of mechanical watchmaking.At the heart of this series, richly textured, curved dials that express the soft and supple feel of natural textiles whose use is interwoven into Japan’s culture.  The dial of this the open-heart creation expresses the texture of raw silk yarn through a radial pattern. With its curvature and intricately textured pattern, the dial captures and reflects ambient light to create a heightened sense of depth and beauty. The top of the indexes curve to conform to the dials’ rounded shape, and the minute and seconds hands bend gently toward the markers.This Classic Men's Seiko Presage SPB469J, features an automatic movement, date display within a 40.2mm stainless steel case featuring an exhibition back and is up to 100 meters water resistant.
